	<h2>_("About QR Pearls")</h2>
	<h3>_("Motivation")</h3>
	<p>_("The QR Pearls web app was written to be used in the Tech Lab installation at")
		<a href="http://www.aakb.dk/biblioteker/hovedbiblioteket">
			_("Aarhus Hovedbibliotek")
		</a>
		_("in February, 2013. The Tech Lab installation is a collaboration between")
		<a href="http://www.folkelab.dk/">
			_("Aarhus Folkelab")
		</a>
		_("and")
		<a href="http://www.osaa.dk/">
			_("Open Space Aarhus")</a>.</p>

	<h3>_("Features")</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>_("Automatic or manual QR code version selection")</li>
		<li>_("QR code error correction level selection")</li>
		<li>_("Preview of generated QR code")</li>
		<li>_("Generates PDF file with beads design")</li>
		<li>_("Mirrored beads design, so QR code is ironed on the back, not the front")</li>
		<li>_("UTF-8 text string support")</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>_("Limitations")</h3>
	<p>_("Generated design is intended for use with 29x29 peg boards (e.g. product code")
		<a href="http://www.hamabeads.com/large_square_679.htm">234</a>
		_("from Hama Beads).")</p>

